      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of peerless distinction. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards of preservation. Every aesthetic surface and mechanical component reflects a commitment to excellence that transcends the standard market offering. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than an immaculate driving experience, this listing represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of singular quality.",
