      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) that serves as a benchmark for the chassis. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a dual-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high-torque loads. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no swirl marks, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation, preserving the original cosmoline. Every bushing, link, and damper is in peak operating condition, maintaining the precision of the variable M differential lock and the car's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. This is a true collector-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44800.0,
